0.1.name: wordpress/dimme-calendar
0.1.description:
This is a simple pluging using the custom post types for a calendar. It will show all the posts of the post type selected published or pending in the future in a calendar.

It uses some jquery for the showing of the calender posts. I will select the first upcomming item first, or else the first thing in the month.
